      <div class="msgContentFrame">Hi there i have a question for all you Armorers out there... <br /> <br />first... how many of you also become a weaver or tanner? <br /> <br />and for those of you who are not weavers or tanners... what do you need from weavers or tanners? <br /> <br />i just want to get an idea on what the market needs so i know who i should sell</div>
      <div class="msgFtFrame">
        <div class="msgFtFrameFix"></div>
